{"tid":966499,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國法律文件 正式出現第三性別選項","createTime":"2019-01-03T00:17:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T00:32:51.000Z","uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bfec3bdc2cbc4a488d12b4756f35dea1f300cb3e","tid":966499,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T00:17:49.000Z","msg":"德國法律文件 正式出現第三性別選項<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6-%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%80%A7%E5%88%A5%E9%81%B8%E9%A0%85-103033588.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2596%2587%25E4%25BB%25B6-%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25BC%258F%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%258F%25BE%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%2580%25A7%25E5%2588%25A5%25E9%2581%25B8%25E9%25A0%2585-103033588.html&d=HWnlXHF9RxL95jyyV0%2FOqJUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=2ae68e7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6-%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%80%A7%E5%88%A5%E9%81%B8%E9%A0%85-103033588.html</a><br />\n<br />\n「第三性別」已逐漸受到國際重視，德國政府通過法案，並在上個月獲得國會表決支持，今年元旦起，雙性人可以在出生證明等法律文件勾選「第三性別」的選項。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，2017年德國憲法法院要求國會立法，希望為雙性人爭取在法律上的人權，提供這些跨性別的人，除了「男性」和「女性」的兩個選擇外，也可以在具有法律效益，像是出生證明、駕照等正式文件上，勾選「第三性別」的欄位。<br />\n<br />\n對此，有些平權組織認為這個法案還無法充份保障「跨性別人士」的權利，因為這些雙性人必需要有醫生證明，才可以在法律文件上勾選「第三性別」的選項。"},{"pid":"be6765869e7264f01e03c6c8c70c83288905854f","tid":966499,"uid":53466,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T00:18:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6235ab034b782bcd4145aa807f667aea314ffc78","tid":966499,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be6765869e7264f01e03c6c8c70c83288905854f","tid":966499,"uid":53466,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T00:18:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T00:21:08.000Z","msg":"第三性別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a5c6f3e62122489d6b92b44b907ac04d787947","tid":966499,"uid":5523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T00:32:51.000Z","msg":"亡國未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}